{"ID":"20260424101902-9yz316m","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-9yz316m","title":"08_性能_功耗_安全_多核_Chiplet","type":"doc","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-mqg776c","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-mqg776c","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"08 性能、功耗、安全、多核、Chiplet"}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-or1v0b4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-or1v0b4","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"前面七卷主要在回答“怎样把单个 NPU 核与执行链设计顺”。这一卷开始面对更现实的系统问题：就算单核、数据流、编译器、runtime 都设计得不错，系统仍然可能因为性能边界、功耗壳、安全要求、多核协同和封装约束而被迫改变形态。"}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-8u5jihe","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-8u5jihe","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"所以这一卷的核心不是再讲新模块，而是建立一个更高层的判断："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"系统级约束会反过来重塑架构与执行策略"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​。"}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-jw29p6t","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-jw29p6t","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1. 先统一一个视角：系统不是追单指标，而是追可持续最优点"}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-ti31nze","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-ti31nze","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"NPU 系统真正优化的不是某个孤立峰值，而是一组互相拉扯的目标："}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-p2r2dmv","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-p2r2dmv","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-u5zdfot","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-u5zdfot","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-nk3tlj3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-nk3tlj3","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"吞吐"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-p16x9co","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-p16x9co","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-548fjvf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-548fjvf","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"单请求延迟"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-ekwgk2y","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-ekwgk2y","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-21jq8d6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-21jq8d6","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"功耗与热"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-7edhysd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-7edhysd","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-snvwubx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-snvwubx","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"面积与成本"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-8yrry4r","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-8yrry4r","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-s6eb4g4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-s6eb4g4","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"安全与隔离"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-sg3cbqr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-sg3cbqr","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-biiaxwn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-biiaxwn","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"可扩展性"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-zm1hwsi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-zm1hwsi","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这意味着："}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-yfsxnyg","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-yfsxnyg","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-d2xja0a","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-d2xja0a","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-t0fkvts","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-t0fkvts","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"再加一个阵列，可能提升峰值，却压垮热和供电"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-81dl68f","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-81dl68f","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-a93dxjy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-a93dxjy","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"再加多核，可能提升总吞吐，却让互联和同步变成新瓶颈"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-v1nwgmd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-v1nwgmd","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-julwko1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-julwko1","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"再加安全隔离，可能提升可信度，却增加延迟和复杂度"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-hv0jx8q","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-hv0jx8q","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-g3seii8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-g3seii8","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"再做 Chiplet，可能缓解大芯片制造难题，却引入新的封装和带宽成本"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-c116gl6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-c116gl6","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"所以系统级设计不是“把所有优点都叠上去”，而是找一组场景约束下最稳的折中点。"}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-2ezp9ky","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-2ezp9ky","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2. 性能分析：先分清峰值、有效值和端到端值"}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-x8n77cl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-x8n77cl","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"看 NPU 性能，至少要区分三种指标："}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-yy0xhh3","Type":"NodeTable","TableAligns":[0,0],"Properties":{"colgroup":"|","id":"20260424101902-yy0xhh3","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableHead","Data":"thead","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"th","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"指标"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"th","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"问的是什么"}]}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"峰值算力"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"理论上阵列满载时一秒能做多少操作"}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"有效硬件吞吐"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"真实层执行时阵列、DMA、buffer 协同后能达到多少"}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"端到端性能"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"连同 runtime、驱动、预后处理、同步一起看，系统一秒能交付多少任务"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-8wdv6yw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-8wdv6yw","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"很多性能误判都来自把这三者混成一个数。"}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-qic3qca","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-qic3qca","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"真正分析性能时，至少要同时看："}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-lqqvi0p","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-lqqvi0p","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-sspw3bo","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-sspw3bo","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-xlrbeo4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-xlrbeo4","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"计算受限还是带宽受限"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-f962wmb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-f962wmb","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-m7bq8i1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-m7bq8i1","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"算子级热点在哪里"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-52xxiu3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-52xxiu3","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-rjisjw3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-rjisjw3","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"多久在等数据"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-su5tzzw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-su5tzzw","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-iqyb2m4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-iqyb2m4","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"多久在等同步"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-rfaesxy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-rfaesxy","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-9jisnao","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-9jisnao","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"多久花在非 NPU 计算上"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-50efy91","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-50efy91","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"所以性能评测不只是跑 benchmark，更是分层定位。"}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-xzx7e5r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-xzx7e5r","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"官方 benchmark 页面最容易被误读。以 Coral 的 Edge TPU benchmark 为例，官方明确提醒了三件事："}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-zlshtfz","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-zlshtfz","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-veyhbra","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-veyhbra","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-0vuxy03","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-0vuxy03","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不同模型的 demand 不同，同一颗 Edge TPU 不会给所有网络同样的收益"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-cubivgd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-cubivgd","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-1sttjbg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-1sttjbg","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果是 USB Accelerator，结果还会受到 host CPU、USB 速率和其他系统资源影响"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-ifmxg0u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-ifmxg0u","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-msc5igg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-msc5igg","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"表里的数字只统计模型执行本身，不包含输入预处理，而且公开 Python 脚本会因为语言开销慢于 C++ benchmark"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-je84e0y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-je84e0y","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"也就是说，benchmark 的第一职责不是证明“平台有多强”，而是先钉住测试边界。边界没写清，平台对比很容易失真。"}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-xxx5k78","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-xxx5k78","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3. Benchmark、PMC、Timeline：工具不是配套，而是设计闭环的一部分"}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-j4819fy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-j4819fy","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"成熟的性能分析通常靠三类工具闭环："}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-iduxndg","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-iduxndg","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3.1 Benchmark"}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-ywv9dzt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-ywv9dzt","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"负责回答："}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-ec83kh8","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-ec83kh8","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-n57kocb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-n57kocb","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-d9m4yr3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-d9m4yr3","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"单算子性能怎样"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-12vpn75","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-12vpn75","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-9jzfa07","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-9jzfa07","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"模型端到端性能怎样"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-d1ecdpm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-d1ecdpm","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-u3gmc2i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-u3gmc2i","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不同输入 shape、batch、精度下变化怎样"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-yp4oypb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-yp4oypb","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"但 benchmark 还必须分清冷启动和热启动。OpenVINO NPU 官方文档把这件事直接拆成两种指标："}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-fovrvcn","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-fovrvcn","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-94n9u58","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-94n9u58","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-o5em5pb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-o5em5pb","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"FEIL"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-epguf4d","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-epguf4d","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-cuk51pt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-cuk51pt","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-58piqoi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-58piqoi","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"首次编译、装载、初始化并跑出第一次推理的总时延"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-3elebdm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-3elebdm","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-z3v7yzx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-z3v7yzx","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"FIL"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-0tl17v4","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-0tl17v4","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children"